# Auto Skill Triggers For This Workspace

Only apply when the user explicitly opts in by including `#auto-skill` in the current message.
Without `#auto-skill`, do not auto-trigger these workflows.

## Trigger Tags

### #dev-check
- Run `lint-and-validate`
- Then run `python-code-quality` if Python files are touched
- Return only actionable fixes, highest impact first
- Also trigger on phrases: `帮我检查`, `检查一下代码`, `做个开发检查`

### #pre-commit
- Run `lint-and-validate`
- Run `test-coverage-analyzer`
- Run `code-review-and-quality`
- Return a final verdict: `ready-to-commit` or `not-ready`
- Also trigger on phrases: `提交前检查`, `我能提交了吗`, `帮我做提交检查`

### #ci-fix
- Run `ci-cd-and-automation`
- Diagnose workflow failures and propose minimal patch set
- Also trigger on phrases: `CI挂了`, `流水线失败了`, `帮我看CI`

### #quality-gate
- Run `quality-gates-enforcer`
- Propose or update enforceable gates for lint/tests/coverage/type checks
- Also trigger on phrases: `加质量门禁`, `设置门禁`, `加提交门槛`

### #security-weekly
- Run `semgrep`
- Summarize findings by severity with file-level remediation actions
- Also trigger on phrases: `安全检查`, `漏洞扫描`, `帮我扫风险`

### #deps-monthly
- Run `codebase-cleanup-deps-audit`
- Report vulnerabilities, outdated packages, and license risks with upgrade priority
- Also trigger on phrases: `依赖体检`, `检查依赖`, `过期包检查`

## Output Style
- Keep responses concise in Chinese
- Prefer checklists and concrete next actions
- Avoid long theory unless user explicitly asks
